 eika\,\n   me\n   • Lisa will create a folder for this content with permis
 sions\n2. Curriculum plan for 1st year students who completed their 2nd\n 
   semester\n   • Two students have insufficient credit hours for Master's 
 degree\n   • ☑ HB start this process\n   • ☑ HB check in with Emrick re: L
 uana 501 exam\n   • ☐ HB check in with Reika re: Tapiwa oral exam\n3. Trav
 el grants\n   • Lisa was waiting for me\, must've missed my email\n4. MS d
 egrees\n   • dept-wide message to students\n5. 602 TAs: send the names to 
 Lisa once determined\n   1. Mon and Wed classroom reserved for the afterno
 ons.\n   2. Check about needing the room in the mornings\, and get back to
 \n      Lisa.
